Remember to @{b}rate@{ub} all the programs you download from Aminet. To do so, send to
aminet-server@wuarchive.wustl.edu :
     RATE <path> <num>
where <path> is the file you want to judge and <num> is a mark from 0..10
with 10 being the best. You can rate several programs in one mail, but
don't rate your own programs. Example: RATE dev/gui/mui23usr.lha 8

You can do what you want with these pictures, but keep in mind that @{i}the
backgrounds are from Scala Multimedia MM300 which is (c) Scala AS 1993.@{ui}

If you have the time to write an e-mail, I'd like to know if someone
likes/hates/uses this pictures and if you have any comments or suggestions
don't hesitate to make me know, thanks. And, if you like them so much that you
feel I deserve some kind of donation, I'll make my best to accept it! ;^)

@{fg shine}@{bg shadow}Bye!
@{fg text}@{bg back}  @{fg shine}@{bg shadow}Marco.@{fg text}@{bg back}
